{"tid":2212841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂-懲罰黃店系列 低熱量 長通心粉沙律","createTime":"2020-09-22T06:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T12:50:20.000Z","uid":30742,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"be806480a8ec4fb003ed2eea684d1d88003965a3","tid":2212841,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T06:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TB76fjy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTB76fjy.jpg&h=b00d7fdc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OTBjxu6Wzxs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOTBjxu6Wzxs&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=139af12c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OTBjxu6Wzxs</a><br />\n<br />\n其實好多黃色小店好需要我地支持同關注<br />\n今次同Hmarket合作，會做一系列食譜比大家<br />\n由簡單都複雜d既都有<br />\n希望可以幫到手<br />\n<br />\n呢次由最簡單既長通粉沙律開始&hellip;&hellip; <br />\n佢呢隻紅米長通粉係無Gluten 無蛋無小麥 <br />\n比一般長通粉低熱量一d <br />\n所以我配左低熱量一d既沙律醬 <br />\n但食落味道口感完全無分別的！  <br />\n大家唔買都記得like and share!!!   <br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://www.hmarket.com.hk/index.php?route=product/product&amp;path=273&amp;product_id=515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hmarket.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dproduct%2Fproduct%26path%3D273%26product_id%3D515&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=8fe362b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hmarket.com.hk/index.php?route=product/product&amp;path=273&amp;product_id=515</a> <br />\n圖文食譜：<a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/09/organic-gluten-free-penne-pasta-salad.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F09%2Forganic-gluten-free-penne-pasta-salad.html&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEVLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=bca4ad2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2020/09/organic-gluten-free-penne-pasta-salad.html</a><br />\n<br />\nSUBSCRIBE AND SHARE!!!!  <br />\nFacebook專頁 :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://w